room_title: Escape room "The Hidden Elixir" by Ozark Escape in Fayetteville (AR)
room_address: 509 W. Spring Street, Suite 140, Fayetteville, AR 72701
room_description: You are acolytes of a powerful wizard. The enemies of your master have poisoned you. You know your master's study holds an antidote. You have one hour to find it before you die.
